tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE women_rights_advocacy_organizations (
    organization_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    organization_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    location VARCHAR(100),
    founding_year INT,
    mission_statement TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE initiatives (
    initiative_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    organization_id INT REFERENCES women_rights_advocacy_organizations(organization_id),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE initiatives ( 
    init_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
    init_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, 
    start_date DATE, 
    end_date DATE, 
    org_id INT REFERENCES organizations(org_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE members ( 
    member_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
    member_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, 
    member_email VARCHAR(100), 
    start_date DATE, 
    org_id INT REFERENCES organizations(org_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE initiatives (
  initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  initiative_name VARCHAR(255),
  initiative_description TEXT,
  org_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (org_id) REFERENCES organizations(org_id)
);

CREATE TABLE initiative_impact (
  impact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  initiative_id INT,
  metric_id INT,
  impact_value DECIMAL,
  FOREIGN KEY (initiative_id) REFERENCES initiatives(initiative_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (metric_id) REFERENCES impact_metrics(metric_id)
);

CREATE TABLE reports (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  report_title VARCHAR(255),
  report_date DATE,
  initiative_id INT,
  impact_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (initiative_id) REFERENCES initiatives(initiative_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (impact_id) REFERENCES initiative_impact(impact_id)
);
